<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Event Update Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 25px;
      border-left: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      padding: 15px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #666;
      border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    .highlight {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #1976d2;
    }
    .change-item {
      padding: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
      border-left: 4px solid #1976d2;
    }
    .event-details {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #1976d2;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    table td {
      padding: 8px;
    }
    table td:first-child {
      font-weight: bold;
      width: 30%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Event Update Notification</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear <%= recipientName %>,</p>
      
      <p>We're writing to inform you that the event <span class="highlight"><%= eventName %></span> has been updated.</p>
      
      <% if (changedFields && changedFields.length > 0) { %>
        <p>The following changes have been made:</p>
        <div style="margin: 15px 0;">
          <% changedFields.forEach(function(change) { %>
            <div class="change-item">
              <strong><%= change.field %>:</strong> "<%= change.oldValue %>" â†’ "<%= change.newValue %>"
            </div>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <p>The event details have been updated.</p>
      <% } %>
      
      <div class="event-details">
        <h3>Current Event Details</h3>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Event Name:</td>
            <td><%= eventName %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Date:</td>
            <td><%= eventDate %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Time:</td>
            <td><%= eventStartTime %> to <%= eventFinishTime %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Type:</td>
            <td><%= eventType %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Mode:</td>
            <td><%= eventMode %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Mode:</td>
            <td><%= eventVenue %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Status:</td>
            <td><%= eventStatus %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please review these updates at your earliest convenience.</p>
      
      <center><a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="button">View Event Details</a></center>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about these changes, please contact the organization's administrators.</p>
      
      <p>Best regards,<br>
      The EventLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> EventLink. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>